        │
        ▼
Test Scenario Design
        │
        ▼
Manual Test Case Design
        │
        ▼
Manual Test Execution
        │
        ▼
Defect Reporting
        │
        ▼
UI Validation
        │
        ▼
REST API Testing
        │
        ▼
API Automation (Newman)
        │
        ▼
Execution Report
```

